{"tid":2436672,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"2010年撐超區方案 梁愛詩今質疑選委不應有區議員 料再延9月立會選舉","createTime":"2021-03-07T10:21:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T13:10:03.000Z","uid":82938,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a3d8961ef965258154acd48b34251e27d34fe76b","tid":2436672,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T10:21:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210307/3OZGXQAQNBF6ZFKGHSRX7DIWS4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2GKcoCxsG-cIvtsxWGLZWwWtJ9MWdAGU2zrB_6GjnJ4MFm2XsY0hshoIE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210307%2F3OZGXQAQNBF6ZFKGHSRX7DIWS4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2GKcoCxsG-cIvtsxWGLZWwWtJ9MWdAGU2zrB_6GjnJ4MFm2XsY0hshoIE&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bE2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=f6fb65ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210307%2F3OZGXQAQNBF6ZFKGHSRX7DIWS4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2GKcoCxsG-cIvtsxWGLZWwWtJ9MWdAGU2zrB_6GjnJ4MFm2XsY0hshoIE&h=6dd27034\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210307/3OZGXQAQNBF6ZFKGHSRX7DIWS4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2GKcoCxsG-cIvtsxWGLZWwWtJ9MWdAGU2zrB_6GjnJ4MFm2XsY0hshoIE</a><br />\n<br />\n黃： 55-60%<br />\n藍：40-45%<br />\n<br />\n藍立法會（even未DQ前）佔3/5 議席<br />\n無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ab384d7d67cf76027f3607882a34068decde95","tid":2436672,"uid":357031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T11:01:22.000Z","msg":"知己知彼, 百戰百勝......原來伍淑清係.....<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1642481\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1642481</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n基本法委員會副主任梁愛詩同全國政協常委伍淑清兩人關係好好，尋日佢哋不約而同出席一個活動，兩人就展現佢哋嘅默契。佢哋離開時，梁愛詩成為採訪對象，伍淑清就自動波幫詩姐拎住啲個人物品......"},{"pid":"d405660832e423a840833ac570a1968e9d86d921","tid":2436672,"uid":112747,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T11:01:29.000Z","msg":"立法會選舉中得票40%既人<br />\n能夠有60%既(立法會)議席<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d9d29cda9e978cfef97ea8adf1d6be09b87630c","tid":2436672,"uid":117509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d405660832e423a840833ac570a1968e9d86d921","tid":2436672,"uid":112747,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T11:01:29.000Z","msg":"立法會選舉中得票40%既人<br />\n能夠有60%既(立法會)議席<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T11:02:59.000Z","msg":"正想咁講<br />\n完全雙重標準"},{"pid":"7b11761535a660fabf298203eff38691c997eb2f","tid":2436672,"uid":357031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T11:04:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_504325_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_504325_0&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bE2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=b3df7ce9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_504325_0&h=b904c7f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_504325_0</a><br />\n20170428<br />\n//【中環人語●聖心妹揭秘】造皇后者同房密斟 林鄭「師姑庵」內搵班底<br />\n<br />\n全國政協常委兼美心太子女伍淑清，與